                    style: TextStyle(
                      fontSize: 11,
                      color: _confidenceColor(message.confidence!),
                      fontWeight: FontWeight.w700,
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            if ((message.meta ?? '').isNotEmpty)
              Padding(
                padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 6),
